FluidSurveys,provides,tools,to,easily,create,online,surveys,Using,the,FluidSurveys,API,developers,can,build,their,own,applications,around,FluidSurveys,tools,The,API,contains,methods,to,retrieve,surveys,and,responses,create,surveys,and,even,create,new,users,A,language,parameter,can,be,provided,that,will,translate,the,data,being,returned,and,all,data,is,returned,in,either,xml,or,json,format